Subject: Denylist created are not reflecting under the CAP
Description:
1. We created a Denylist for "Email Domain" and wanted to include that under one CAP. But we don't see the Email Domain options while creating the CAP.

2. We created a Denylist for the "Application" and wanted to include that under one CAP. We can enable that, but we don't see that policy mapped when we edit the policy again. It also creates the problem in deleting the policy.
Solution_Comment__c: This case is now closed as the fix is scheduled for release of Endpoint Protector 5.9.5.0.
